### 限制的测试
#### 1. 限制 mock fk parent table 和子表不能跨库。
use xf_foreign_key_checks_test_db_2;
set foreign_key_checks = off;
create table tc_flashback_rename_1(c1 int, c2 int, constraint fk_tp_flashback_rename_1_tc_flashback_rename_1 foreign key(c1, c2) references xf_foreign_key_checks_test_db.xxxxxxxxx(c1, c2));
ERROR 0A000: parent table and child table in foreign key belong to different databases not supported
create table tc_flashback_rename_1(c1 int, c2 int);
alter table tc_flashback_rename_1 add constraint fk_tp_flashback_rename_1_tc_flashback_rename_1 foreign key(c1, c2) references xf_foreign_key_checks_test_db.xxxxxxxxx(c1, c2);
ERROR 0A000: parent table and child table in foreign key belong to different databases not supported
#### 2. 限制 alter table rename 出现和 mock 父表的同名 real 父表时，alter table 中不允许有其他 actions，详见 2-2-4 alter table rename to 测试部分。

